  "title": "Devotional: Reflection: God's Role in Growth and Talent",
  "body": "God loves us as a Father. He wants to see us mature, to succeed both on and off the mats. But it’s His will — not ours — that determines how far we go and how long we last. Whatever skill you have, even just enough autism to win NAGA, is a gift. Don’t forget where it came from.",
